            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1681804056146-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> to a bowl with 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your<strong> tomato sauce</strong></p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
