        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>from the oven and add the <strong>pizza bases</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> between the <strong>pizza bases </strong>and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p>",
