    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pizzas are cooking, peel and finely slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to a small bowl with the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p>",
