    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> mayo</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>remaining grated garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a small bowl with a small splash of <strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>chilli sauce</strong></p>",
