    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, drizzle the <strong>garlic mayo</strong> and <strong>chilli sauce </strong>over the <strong>pizzas</strong> and top with the <strong>quick-pickled shallots</strong> – these are your <strong>doner kebab pizzas</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>doner kebab pizzas</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
